## Required workflow

For every task:

1. Read the full task packet.
2. Identify relevant files before editing.
3. Restate the implementation plan briefly.
4. Make the smallest coherent change.
5. Add or update tests when behavior changes.
6. Run required validation.
7. Review your own diff.
8. Return an execution report using `docs/ai/codex-report-template.md`.

## Scope control

Do not:

- rewrite unrelated code;
- rename public APIs unless required;
- change formatting across unrelated files;
- update dependencies unless explicitly requested;
- introduce new frameworks without approval;
- remove tests instead of fixing them;
- silence errors without explaining why.

